comments: Westbrook (LAL) reaches in and makes incidental hand on ball contact with Ibaka (LAC) when the ball is dislodged.
Johnson (LAL) and Ibaka (LAC) mutually engage in marginal contact prior to disengaging during the rebound.
Ibaka's (LAC) arm makes marginal contact with Ariza (LAL) during the rebound, Ibaka does not dislodge Ariza.
Correctly called 5 Second Violation on Batum (LAC).
Davis (LAL) establishes a legal position in Jackson's (LAC) path and marginal contact occurs during the pick.
Ibaka (LAC) makes contact to Monk's (LAL) arm during his put back shot attempt near the rim.
Davis (LAL) establishes a legal position in Batum's (LAC) path and marginal contact occurs during the pick.
Ibaka (LAC) wraps his arm around Ariza's (LAL) front off ball which affects his ability to defend the oncoming driving shot attempt.
Ibaka (LAC) and Davis (LAL) mutually engage in marginal contact as both players move down the lane.
Morris Sr. (LAC) rotates over and briefly places two hands on Davis (LAL) as he starts his dribble, the contact is marginal.
Batum (LAC) briefly places two hands on Davis (LAL) as he disengages from the pick, Batum immediately removes his hands and the contact is marginal.
Reaves (LAL) makes marginal contact to Jackson's (LAC) off arm that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Mann (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position during Davis' (LAL) driving shot attempt.
